metadata.name: ApeVerse NFT Collection #1
metadata.description: ApeVerse, as the name suggest it's a metaverse of Ape NFTs. It's been rudimentary that ape NFTs are currently dominating the NFT market and because of it's stunning design, people can't get enough of it. But the main drawback is that many NFT enthusiasts have missed out on a lot of projects and it has now become unaffordable. Well ApeVerse is here to save you the pain in searching for these projects, with a mind-blowing 2222 limited Ape NFTs, with future metaverse integration, NFT marketplace and memetech, it's going to be one of the leading NFT platforms out there.
